Hi Everyone, I have two HS entities. One is for development and another one for production. I am working on HubDB related work. I have mentioned Table ID in the HTML of the one of my modules. I had created this on development server. When I tried to push it to production server, it is not getting uploaded.

I tried hs upload and Github Actions. Nothing worked. Can anyone help me?

I got the error saying "InvalidArgumentException: 1st argument with value '568XXXXXX' must be a valid table ID or name"
